														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1149784">
									

<p>The only cannon is <a href="/scp-044">SCP-044</a>.</p>
<p>If you create an SCP with logs, wait a day or two to find out if it's going to be down voted out of existence.</p>
<p>Don't just create a log for an existing SCP because you think it needs it without commenting in the discussion thread for that SCP first. Authors and senior staff have approval over that. Reversions for that sort of thing are sudden and may (or may NOT) come with a moderator warning.</p>

